                        <interp inst="t18400406-name-192" type="given" value="LEWIS"></interp>LEWIS SHORT</persName>
                  </hi>. I am the brother of Henry Short—I went in pursuit and found the prisoner in Bethnal-green-road with his mother and brother—I told him he had been taking some shoes from the shop—he cried, and said he was sorry.</p>
